T02TD1615E:142a-1: badzra ghanta p'u dza kra ma s'a dha nam /
T02TD1615E:142a-3: rdo rje dril thabs kyis mchod pa'i thabs kyi rim pa //
T02TD1615E:142a-4: dpal rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1615E:142a-5: sgrib gnyis spong zhing tshogs gnyis bsgrub //
T02TD1615E:142a-6: mchod pa dag la rtag dga' phyir //
T02TD1615E:142a-7: rdo rje dril bu'i sgrub pa ni //
T02TD1615E:142a-8: bde mchog gsad la btud de bshad //
T02TD1615E:142a-9: yid dang mthun zhing dben gnas su //
T02TD1615E:142a-10: yang dag don ldan rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD1615E:142a-11: rdo rje dril bu byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1615E:142a-12: mdzes pa'i mandala steng dag tu //
T02TD1615E:142a-13: me tog tshom bu gnyis bzhag ste //
T02TD1615E:142a-14: rdo rje dril bu steng du bzhag / dang por dag pa'i khrus bya ste //
T02TD1615E:142a-15: mos pa tsam gyis lhar bskyed nas //
T02TD1615E:142a-16: 'od kyis brtag gnyis sbyang bya ste //
T02TD1615E:142a-17: stong pa'i ngang las a'a:h'um bskyed //
T02TD1615E:142a-18: de nas rdo rje dril bu gnyis //
T02TD1615E:142a-19: de nas dpal ldan yab yum bskyed //
T02TD1615E:142a-20: de la ye shes 'khor lo gzhug / gnyis med bstim nas dbang bskur zhing //
T02TD1615E:142a-21: byin gyis brlabs nas mchod cing bstod //
T02TD1615E:142a-22: de 'od zhu las rdor dril gyur //
T02TD1615E:142a-23: bzlas pa byas nas blang bar bya //
T02TD1615E:142a-24: g-yon gyis steng 'og tshul du blang //
T02TD1615E:142a-25: de nas g-yas su rdo rje blang //
T02TD1615E:142a-26: snying ga dag tu bzung nas ni //
T02TD1615E:142a-27: dril bu g-yon gyi dku ru bsten //
T02TD1615E:142a-28: de nas g-yon du gar bcas te //
T02TD1615E:142a-29: g-yas la thug pa dgu ru bskor //
T02TD1615E:142b-0: de nas gong @142b bzhin gzung bar bya //
T02TD1615E:142b-1: dang po thun mong bshad bya ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-2: gar bskor rdo rje dril bu gnyis //
T02TD1615E:142b-3: gong bzhin 'dzin pa bca' ba ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-4: de nas dril bu len gsum dkrol //
T02TD1615E:142b-5: de nas gnyis kas lan gsum ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-6: tha mas steng du bskor nas ni //
T02TD1615E:142b-7: gar bskor gong bzhin 'dzin pa ni//
T02TD1615E:142b-8: kun gyi sngon du 'gro ba yin //
T02TD1615E:142b-9: ba dan phyar ba'i rnam pa la //
T02TD1615E:142b-11: rdo dril gsor gsil bcas pa la //
T02TD1615E:142b-12: gnyis ka 'dzin pa sbyor min te //
T02TD1615E:142b-13: dkrol ba ba dan g-yob pa la //
T02TD1615E:142b-14: dang po la sogs lugs bzhin te //
T02TD1615E:142b-15: ba dan mi g-yo ba bting pa la//
T02TD1615E:142b-16: mi dkrol mi gsor so ru bzhag / ba dan 'gugs pa'i dus dag tu //
T02TD1615E:142b-17: dran pa chu bur bzhin du dkrol //
T02TD1615E:142b-18: sems can don brtson gyur pa na //
T02TD1615E:142b-19: mdung thabs zhes ni bya ba ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-20: nyon mongs tha ba 'bigs pa'i tshul //
T02TD1615E:142b-21: dang po dril bu gsum yin te //
T02TD1615E:142b-23: g-yon du gnyi gas byed pa yin //
T02TD1615E:142b-24: sgrib pa gnyis ni 'joms pa ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-25: lan gsum bskor ba dngos grub len //
T02TD1615E:142b-26: steng du bskor ba brtan par byed //
T02TD1615E:142b-27: snying gar bzung bas bkrag mdangs bskyed //
T02TD1615E:142b-28: don grub sbyor ba bshad bya ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-29: g-yas kyis rgya gram sbyor ba dang //
T02TD1615E:142b-30: g-yon dang dbus kyi sbyor ba ni //
T02TD1615E:142b-31: sku gsung thugs kyi sbyor ba ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-32: snying ga la ni rten par byed //
T02TD1615E:142b-33: dril bu'i cha la rab brtags nas //
T02TD1615E:142b-34: spyi bo mgrin pa snying ga yi //
T02TD1615E:142b-35: thad kar 'dzin cing bskor ba ni //
T02TD1615E:142b-36: sa 'og sa bla sa steng gi / srid gsum sprul pas 'grub pa'o //
T02TD1615E:142b-37: rdo rje sems 'gugs sbyor ba la //
T02TD1615E:142b-38: dang por phar la spros pa ni //
T02TD1615E:142b-39: rang gi mchod pa byed pa ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-40: snying gar 'gugs pa dngos grub len //
T02TD1615E:142b-41: rdo rje bsnol brtan zhes bya ba //
T02TD1615E:142b-42: gnyis ka'i dbang du byas pa ste //
T02TD1615E:142b-43: kar 'dzin gnyis kyi thad ka ru //
T02TD1615E:142b-45: g-yas brtan pa ni thabs yin te //
T02TD1615E:142b-46: g-yon brtan pa ni shes rab yin //
T02TD1615E:142b-47: gnyis brtan pa ni sbyor ba'o //
T02TD1615E:142b-48: gong du sbyor ba'i byang chub sems //
T02TD1615E:142b-49: gnyis brtan nas ni 'bul bar byed //
T02TD1615E:142b-50: de yis rgyal ba thams cad mnyes //
T02TD1615E:142b-51: rol pa'i cho ga byed pa ni //
T02TD1615E:143a-2: shes rab ye shes gnas skabs dang //
T02TD1615E:143a-3: gsang ba yi ni spyod pa dang //
T02TD1615E:143a-4: gsang ba'i spyod pa'i skabs su shod //
T02TD1615E:143a-5: gzhan yang yon tan brjod las 'das //
T02TD1615E:143a-6: bla med gsang ba'i bla na med //
T02TD1615E:143a-7: gtso bo mchog gi las sbyor ba //
T02TD1615E:143a-8: khyad par gyi ni bshad bya ste //
T02TD1615E:143a-9: dang po'i las dang tha ma'i las //
T02TD1615E:143a-10: gong ma bzhin te thun mong ngo //
T02TD1615E:143a-12: snying gar 'dzin pas shes par bya //
T02TD1615E:143a-13: mdun du spos phor 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD1615E:143a-14: gyen la me tog 'thor ba dang //
T02TD1615E:143a-15: sor mo mar me'i tshul du bsgreng //
T02TD1615E:143a-16: gdengs pas byug pa'i tshul du byug / mnyes pa yi ni thabs su bshad //
T02TD1615E:143a-17: zhi ba yi ni sbyor ba ste //
T02TD1615E:143a-18: rdo rje dri bu'i thad bzung nas //
T02TD1615E:143a-19: gang la phog pas de byed bsam //
T02TD1615E:143a-20: rgyas pa steng du 'phyar ba ste //
T02TD1615E:143a-21: ye shes khams gsum bcud len byed //
T02TD1615E:143a-22: dbang ni gyen la phyogs nas su //
T02TD1615E:143a-24: drag po gsang ba'i cho ga ni //
T02TD1615E:143a-25: gdul bya mdun du gnas pa la //
T02TD1615E:143a-27: rengs pa yi ni sbyor ba ste //
T02TD1615E:143a-28: gdul bya mdun du bas ma bya ste //
T02TD1615E:143a-29: gyen thur thad kar phyar ba yis //
T02TD1615E:143a-30: spyi bo rkang pa'i bar dag tu //
T02TD1615E:143a-31: rdo rje ring po bsgeng [*bsgreng?] bar byed //
T02TD1615E:143a-32: bstab pa'i cho ga'i las byed pa //
T02TD1615E:143a-33: rdo rje gdengs ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1615E:143a-34: thur bsags la ni len pa ste //
T02TD1615E:143a-35: gyen du phyar nas bteg byas nas //
T02TD1615E:143a-36: de nas mdun du bstan pa'o //
T02TD1615E:143a-37: de la sogs pa'i sbyor ba mchog / gsang ba de nyid rjes 'brangs nas //
T02TD1615E:143a-38: blo dman don du bshad pa yin //
T02TD1615E:143a-39: 'di la nyes par gyur pa kun //
T02TD1615E:143a-40: 'phags dang mkhas la bzod par gsol //
T02TD1615E:143a-41: bdag gis 'di brtsams bsod nams kyis //
T02TD1615E:143a-42: khams gsum thams cad bla med shog / rdo rje dril thabs kyis mchod pa'i rim pa slob dpon 'phags pa ltas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
